{"tid":2515224,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[畫鞋] 畫咗個深海寶箱上對鞋度","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T23:21:10.000Z","uid":202514,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49dbacec42185bc567ba4fb19ac61dbb07c80367","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:16:46.000Z","msg":"Hi，又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次post返舊作<br />\n就係每次有人問襟唔襟用我都攞出來講嘅嗰對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfRRhFhnR6GemmEYJkgkfTKGiYQncZ6vQuhKhat2htGgQ?filename=Np54dZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNp54dZW.jpg&h=11c2869a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQBwbjoSUj1dLzRxk7VtvXimj2ZoxPQcxWJDUTPJszbEd?filename=cVoYirD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcVoYirD.jpg&h=0b28eea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本個樣係咁<br />\n純灰白銀三色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcbJHXgwzKGutY4t9rCQRv7odhDp7Ryz2fkrA3XKW9JdH?filename=3AoENjZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3AoENjZ.jpg&h=9213086a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始淨係想畫木紋，但唔知畫咩主題好<br />\n因為呢對鞋會自動綁鞋帶<br />\n綁嗰陣個feel好似八爪魚腳勒緊咁<br />\n聯想埋一齊之後就諗到畫深海寶箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加左啲細節比如藤壺、生銹嘅寶箱嗰條鐵邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXRnZDzSMDaMMm345PvyYprRoz339WQ22bWkgVaC7aoWW?filename=2W4gPzA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2W4gPzA.jpg&h=3c918658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNU8Ng1w3siRAf3jyeqDaLj3qmzB2797jjdjk38sj4wSL?filename=r2K1geC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2K1geC.jpg&h=1352029a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbiEZQbKX7nTKDcNq2kyXgZXjmS6nMVc2fzVhmTc9Dkz6?filename=7fGfkGi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fGfkGi.jpg&h=957977f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbAms3gM3dgRV8s7fAmHzPQyRDU8f99sobEpVaXSevuS4?filename=3LhNWeD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LhNWeD.jpg&h=efb54035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYb4GHPjEogZi2vLm2A7XnmadufAJN7acpAbcW5n99qFo?filename=jg5cnUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjg5cnUD.jpg&h=675470ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWf6z5KFXnLckSCxirqh6BHV5Qc1LZ9eRVhS4qSaPPuqH?filename=05HaT1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05HaT1k.jpg&h=473f68e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得唔錯嘅話，可以支持下小弟<br />\nFollow返個ig : yauyau_jy<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/yauyau_jy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyauyau_jy&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=6048d631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/yauyau_jy</a><br />\n<br />\n不定期會有改鞋嘅post/story"},{"pid":"8bffad7ba9ec451f787f9337accf565a83ce8cbb","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6b2a901b2fa3ae0aca4eef98111a733d988b24","tid":2515224,"uid":202514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl